The Odds API (Recommended)
This is probably your best bet for a free option:

Free Tier: 500 requests/month
Endpoint: https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports/americanfootball_nfl/odds
Coverage: Moneylines, spreads, totals from major books (DraftKings, FanDuel, BetMGM, Caesars, etc.)
Format: JSON
Documentation: https://the-odds-api.com/sports-odds-data/nfl-odds.html

Example Request:
GET https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports/americanfootball_nfl/odds?regions=us&markets=h2h,spreads,totals&oddsFormat=american&apiKey=YOUR_API_KEY